Wade King
11/03/2017

To compile/run:

	make
	./assn2 [obj file]
	
Controls:
	w: switch between wireframe and polygon fill
	e: switch to/from scale mode
		w: increase scale
		s: increase scale
		a: decrease scale
		d: decrease scale
	r: switch to/from rotate mode
		w: rotate counterclockwise around y axis
		s: rotate clockwise around y axis
		a: rotate clockwise around x axis
		d: rotate counterclockwise around x axis		
	t: switch to/from translate mode
		w: translate up
		s: translate down
		a: translate left
		d: translate right
	esc: exit program
			
Files:
	Camera.h
	Camera.cpp
	main.cpp
	Makefile
	Matrix.cpp
	Matrix.h
	Object.cpp
	Object.h
